<p><font color="#669900"><b>YaST - The All-in-One System Assistant</b></font></p>
<p>The SUSE LINUX configuration and administration tool YaST is subject to ongoing development. Use YaST to connect to the network, replace the sound card or printer, or create a user account for a new family member. All of this is easy for YaST - and easy for you!</p>
<p>With YaST, administrative tasks can be performed from the text console or by way of the comfortabe graphical user interface. YaST is suitable for both newcomers and experts.</p>
